Re: 怖くないと。。。。?
by Harisenbon » Thu 06.10.2010 9:22 pm I think seeing the clip would clear it up alot, but here's my take on it:ガンが怖い？死ぬの怖い？Are you scared of cancer?Are you scared of dying?怖くないと・・・(怖くないといったら?）"What would it mean if I said I wasn't scared..."Maybe?
