Re: 怖くないと。。。。?
by NileCat » Fri 06.11.2010 10:33 am Although there are a couple of possibilities, I for one assume that:（私が） 怖くないと（でも）（あなたは思うのか）？＝　（怖いさ、もちろん）And both of Hyperworm's and Harisenbon's sound fine to me too.
